FT  07 JUN 93 / Observer: Gatt tactics
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Virtually everyone agrees that Peter Sutherland, the EC's nominee and former
EC competition commissioner, would make a first-class director-general of
the General Agreement on Tariffs and Trade. So what is to be made of the
last-minute shenanigans in the run-up to Wednesday's election of Gatt's new
